{"tid":1433680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重要) 發夢常識學","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:18:14.000Z","uid":170504,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"074fb6fc8fcdac9b2dd656e4373c1b835dfc68a1","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"發現有一班人有啲野真係唔知<br />\n有班人係分別到狗車,消防,救護車既聲<br />\n總知佢聽到有車聲就驚到跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩大家聽下狗車係點響<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFnRlNIPMB4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsFnRlNIPMB4&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=8ca45f8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFnRlNIPMB4</a><br />\n咁你認到,就可以冷靜分辨<br />\n<br />\n發夢見過有人都係唔帶口罩 <br />\n最後空氣污染嚴重 我唔該大家帶返個口罩<br />\n理解唔到到今時今日仲有人係會唔帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次發夢請大家都帶把長遮<br />\n又可以擋雨可以擋太陽 覆蓋率大 <br />\n唔好再帶縮骨遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後經過琴晚 我諗好多人都有&quot;鐳射槍&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該大家唔好用黎照人類 人類之外既生物我唔理<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都攰 但我地要贏 就要繼續堅持<br />\n最後 發夢既時候請捉住身邊既人 唔好有人落單<br />\n唔想大家俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗仔好惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留返條命返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(物資)珍惜物資同時都唔好亂買!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382321</a><br />\n手足們可唔可以應承我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430309</a><br />\n民意就係我地依邊 但大家可唔可以醒少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417422</a>"},{"pid":"a4c10cbe22c3a8583c593743b9d46629bc775df8","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"開錯台添 點解冇常識台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e6956444d3989e7f1e8f439ddea740bbd322af","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c75dc8de50fd20e6b003deef254260991df8cfc","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d60f3c7e16d5aad08721c1fbb000492ad0cb21f","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"854742c1939d91355817159545a5103c9ed2926a","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aece954e5636cb52fa0d6f63232d6a6daa25c37","tid":1433680,"uid":293346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3cfbc43f4845e960760f9ac6c4f571e48a297b","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce36e6a5edc5c2294b855625c117c162a7cdfbbb","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57adfe2f59a498cb056725d32fd59581c80f7de","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ea5e506dc43046e3e63de661f9be668b36e7957","tid":1433680,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"